6,'http://35.189.50.118/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/aipuck-detail_05.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(356,1,'2018-10-18 06:33:42','2018-10-18 06:33:42','<p>[vc_section][vc_row][vc_column width=\"7/12\"][vc_single_image image=\"257\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"5/12\"][vc_custom_heading source=\"post_title\" font_container=\"tag:div|text_align:left|color:%23777777\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"custom_para\" css=\".vc_custom_1539780824317{margin-top: 30px !important;}\"]AiPUCK is a smart self organizing clustered sensor network for critical perimeter security and surveillance.[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner el_class=\"product_features\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"354\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"The perimeter security system consists of at least four different types of sensors in individual single sensor nodes that interconnect automatically into a tamper proof network of autonomous clusters.\" font_container=\"tag:h6|text_align:left|color:%23000000\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"block_summary\"]-- Sensor nodes include Magnetic, Doppler Radar (plus compass), Audio and Seismic; all have GPS</p>\r\n<p>-- Optional EO mini cameras are available upon request</p>\r\n<p>-- Nodes are simply deployed and \'forgotten\', battery capacity ensures 5 years operation</p>\r\n<p>-- Deployment can be done manually and/or air dropped (drone, helicopter)</p>\r\n<p>-- Sensors are typically 20 to 40 m apart, clusters are 100 -150 m in diameter</p>\r\n<p>-- Sensor auto grouping done using proprietary IP protocol, linked using short range radio communication</p>\r\n<p>-- In each cluster one node is selected as Virtual Cluster Head; in case of malfunction a new one is selected[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"355\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Real Time communication and data handling\" font_container=\"tag:h6|text_align:left|color:%23000000\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"block_summary\"]-- Frequencies available between 300 MHz and 2.4 GHz, adjusted to client specifications</p>\r\n<p>-- All data types gathered, fused/ integrated and analyzed in real time at cluster level</p>\r\n<p>-- Any indication of intrusion is communicated as meta data to the field Command &amp; Control Center</p>\r\n<p>-- Interface protocol is UDP/ XML through an open interface, enabling integration with other detection systems[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_section disable_element=\"yes\"][vc_row][vc_column][vc_raw_html]JTNDaDIlMjBjbGFzcyUzRCUyMmNyZWRhbF9oZWFkaW5nJTIyJTIwc3R5bGUlM0QlMjJtYXJnaW4tYm90dG9tJTNBMzVweCUzQiUyMiUzRURhc2hib2FyZCUzQyUyRmgyJTNF[/vc_raw_html][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"222\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"223\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_section][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text][all_related_services][/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section]</p>\r\n','AiPUCK','','inherit','closed','closed','','246-revision-v1','','','2018-10-18 06:33:42','2018-10-18 06:33:42','',246,'http://35.189.50.118/246-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(357,1,'2018-10-18 07:10:21','2018-10-18 07:10:21','Sed ut perspiciatis unde omnis iste natus error sit voluptatem accusantium doloremque laudantium, totam rem aperiam, eaque ipsa quae ab illo inventore veritatis et quasi architecto beatae vitae dicta sunt explicabo. Nemo enim ipsam voluptatem quia voluptas sit aspernatur aut odit aut fugit, sed quia consequuntur magni dolores eos qui ratione voluptatem sequi nesciunt. Neque porro quisquam est, qui dolorem ipsum quia dolor sit amet, consectetur, adipisci velit, sed quia non n