ass=\"custom_para\"]Our multi-sensor security device, the AiPOD, is built with both commercial and military applications in mind.[/vc_column_text][vc_btn title=\"Read More\" style=\"custom\" custom_background=\"#ffffff\" custom_text=\"#13d1e6\" shape=\"square\" align=\"left\" link=\"url:http%3A%2F%2F35.189.50.118%2Faipod%2F|||\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"5/12\"][vc_single_image image=\"406\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"right\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row gap=\"35\" equal_height=\"yes\" content_placement=\"middle\"][vc_column width=\"5/12\" el_class=\"wwd-content wwd-content-left\"][vc_single_image image=\"407\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"7/12\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Light weight surveillance\" font_container=\"tag:h4|text_align:left|color:%23000000\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"custom_para\"]A lightweight aerial mapping &amp; surveillance and precision targeting drone that can fly a planned mission for up to 90 mins. Highly stable, easy to operate with little training required by the individual, it can carry multiple camera payloads for military encrypted transmission to the Mobile Command &amp; Control Center, as well as a precision grenade warhead.[/vc_column_text][vc_btn title=\"Read More\" style=\"custom\" custom_background=\"#ffffff\" custom_text=\"#13d1e6\" shape=\"square\" align=\"left\" link=\"url:http%3A%2F%2F35.189.50.118%2Flight-weight-surveillance|||\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row gap=\"35\" equal_height=\"yes\" content_placement=\"middle\"][vc_column width=\"7/12\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Ultra light surveillance\" font_container=\"tag:h4|text_align:left|color:%23000000\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"custom_para\"]A miniature fixed wing drone carrying an Intelligence, Surveillance &amp; Reconnaissance (ISR) package that is very difficult to detect, recognize or track.[/vc_column_text][vc_btn title=\"Read More\" style=\"custom\" custom_background=\"#ffffff\" custom_text=\"#1